Spotify Christmas Playlists Dataframe

christmas_playlists.Rd

A dataframe containing playlists, track names, and an assortment of numeric and non-numeric variables.

christmas_playlists

Format

A data frame with 226 rows and 26 variables The variables are as follows:

playlist_name

playlist name

playlist_uri

playlist uri

playlist_tracks_url

playlist tracks url

playlist_num_tracks

number of tracks in a given playlist

snapshot_id

snapshot id

playlist_img

playlist img

track_name

track name

track_uri

track uri

artist_name

artist name

album_name

album

album_img

album img

track_popularity

track popularity

daceability

danceability

energy

energy

key

key

loudness

loudness

mode

mode

speechiness

speechiness

acousticness

acoustiness

instrumentalness

instrumentalness

liveness

liveness

valence

valence

tempo

tempo

duration_ms

duration_ms

time_signature

time_signature

key_mode

key_mode

Source

The data was sourced from the Spotify app.
